we go to hockey practice today...and as me and tony are getting out of the car, john come crusing through the parking lot in his beat up truck and crashed into a parked car. he put this huge dent into the back of this car. he keeps driving and parks like...5 feet away from it.(his park job sucked too) we're in the lockeroom and he comes in and dosent say anything..so im like "dude...you know you hit a car, right?" and hes like "no shit, i dont give a fuck." and so i just ignore the stupid comments he makes after that, like how he was driving 70 in a 40 zone blah blah. so we get on the ice do some drills and half way through the drill the owner of hollydell and a cop show up. they go to the highland coach (since we dont have a coach...?!) and ask for john...hes gone...hes probly gonna lose his lisence for hit and...run/go part 5 feet away...and i hope hes banned from hollydell rinks and we never see him again.

wtf, i got caught cheating, basicly the first time i cheated, not ever, but this year...anyway so maths about to start, i pull out my caculater and inside the cover i write the FUCKING RETARDED differences from what alternate interior, same side, and corrasponding angles equal, which adds to the reason why today sucked, I FUCKING JUST WROTE THEM FROM MEMORY!!!(duh..) and as with everything i do, i fucked it up. mr mac calls for a random calculater check, so i quickly erase my data and close it up, he gets to me and takes an extra time examining it...i knew i was busted...so i take the test and i think i did pretty good on it was easy NO FUCKING NEED TO TRY AND CHEAT!!! ha i didnt even use my claculater...so class ends 
"joe can i see you" he says
i choke and reply "me?!" 
"i have reason to believe you were going to cheat"
i gave a discusted look..."yes.."
"your the reason i did that caculater check..." he said...sticking out..his chin(?!)
"i figured. all i wrote was..."
he cut me off, "you should have a zero"
"yea, but i earased it...." he cut me off again
"i dont care, you cant use that calculater anymore, only these."pointing to the shitty class ones
"ok, ill use them, it was stupid i wont do it again..." and i walked out of class laughing.
